snippet.textDisplay:
I'm grateful to be able to enjoy The Weeknd's art at a time where things are undeniably crazy in the world. Best wishes to all of you struggling and having fears dancing around you. In the meantime, I can only imagine being able to thank Abel to the best of my abilities for allowing me to take a breather with such a beautiful album. After Hours and his other music will luckily forever be in my grasp, and now, I am more thankful for it than ever before. I'm speechless and allured by his work, as always, especially now with everything that's going on. It amazes how one person can allow you to sit back and enjoy their music so appreciatively.


Anne
04/08/2020
